Kidney diseases topics

   Each of the topics below exists as a booklet or fact sheet. Copies may
   be ordered from the National Kidney and Urologic Diseases Information
   Clearinghouse.
     * Amyloidosis and Kidney Disease
       (pdf version*)
     * Analgesic Nephropathy: Painkillers and the Kidneys
     * Anemia in Kidney Disease and Dialysis
       (pdf version*)
     * Childhood Nephrotic Syndrome
     * Cystoscopy
     * Diabetes Insipidus
     * Eat Right To Feel Right on Hemodialysis (pdf version*)
     * End-Stage Renal Disease
     * Financial Help for Treatment of Kidney Failure (pdf version*)
     * Glomerular Diseases
     * Goodpasture Syndrome
     * Growth Failure in Children With Kidney Disease
     * Hematuria: Blood in the Urine
     * Hemodialysis (pdf version*)
     * Hemodialysis Dose and Adequacy
       (pdf version*)
     * Hemolytic Uremic Syndrome
     * High Blood Pressure and Kidney Disease
     * IgA Nephropathy
     * Kidney Biopsy
     * Kidney Disease of Diabetes
     * Kidney Diseases Dictionary
     * Kidney Failure
     * Kidney Failure: Choosing a Treatment That's Right for You (pdf
       version*)
     * Kidney Failure Glossary (pdf version)*
     * Kidney Function
     * Kidney Stones in Adults
     * Kidney Transplantation (pdf version*)
     * Lupus Nephritis
     * Medical Tests of Kidney Function
     * Nephrotic Syndrome in Adults
     * Normal Kidney Function
     * Nutrition and Kidney Disease (pdf version*)
     * Peritoneal Dialysis (pdf version*)
     * Peritoneal Dialysis Dose and Adequacy (pdf version*)
     * Polycystic Kidney Disease
     * Proteinuria
     * Pyelonephritis (Kidney Infection) in Adults
     * Renal Nutrition (pdf version*)
     * Renal Osteodystrophy (pdf version*)
     * Renal Tubular Acidosis
     * Simple Kidney Cysts
     * Ureteroscopy
     * Urologic Diseases
     * Vascular Access for Hemodialysis (pdf version*)
     * Vesicoureteral Reflux
     * Your Kidneys and How They Work

