Statistics

     * Kidney and Urologic Diseases Statistics for the United States
       Summary fact sheet of statistics for kidney and urologic diseases.
     * United States Renal Data System
       Comprehensive statistics on kidney failure.
     * Other Sources for Statistics
       Contact information for organizations that provide statistics for
       kidney diseases.

Order forms

   To order copies of the titles above, print the items below and follow
   the instructions included.
     * Kidney and Urologic Diseases Publications Titles
       Provides a complete list of the publications available from the
       National Kidney and Urologic Diseases Information Clearinghouse
       (NKUDIC).
     * Publications Order Form
       Health professionals, patients, and consumers may order single
       copies of most titles in the Publications Titles list free of
       charge. Health professionals may order bulk quantities for a fee.

